name: Verify "Managing Provider" is not able to update the "Caregiver" and validation displays if any mandatory field is not populated while updating the Caregiver And Verify "Managing Provider" is not able to update the "Caregiver" with invalid details And Verify "Managing Provider" is able to update the "Caregiver" details

steps.name: When I click on the second index link Caregivers
Then It redirects on the Active Caregivers screen
When I populate data Auto_Test_Caregiver Autonix in the "Search" field
When I click on the "View or Update" option under the "Action" section
Then It redirects on the Update Caregivers screen
When I update the "Caregiver" but does not populate one of the mandatory field
When I click on the button with text Update
Then validation message Please enter first name appears
When User add 1 in name field
Then validation message Please enter at least 2 characters. appears
When User add 1 in last name field
Then validation message Please enter at least 2 characters. appears
When User add #####gmail.com in email field
When I click on the button with text Update
Then validation message Please enter a valid email address. appears
When User add 1 in mobile number field
When I click on the button with text Update
Then validation message Please enter at least 8 characters. appears
When User add #####gmail.com in mobile number field
Then validation message Please enter a valid number. appears
When User add !@#$%%$#@! ^&^&^& in mobile number field
Then validation message Please enter no more than 16 characters. appears
When I click on the button with text Update
When User add Updated_Auto_Test_Caregiver in name field
When User add Autonix in last name field
When I fill valid and unique data in email
When User add 2026859019 in mobile number field
When User add Parents in relationship field
When User add Florida in State field
When User add Miami in city field
When User add 8900 Canyon Trail Rd in address field
When User add 00123 in zipcode field
When I click on the button with text Update
Then Success message Caregiver details updated ! appears
When I populate data Auto_Test_Caregiver Autonix in the "Search" field
Then Created caregiver should be visible in the list with Updated_Auto_Test_Caregiver Autonix and 2026859019 and Parents and <children> and Active
